summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4498 for the improvement of 39th Avenue Southwest, from West Warsaw Street to West Orchard Street; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by grading and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 52827, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
